[SHORT DESC]
No additional effect.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>There is absolutely no reason to ever run Slam in competitive play. Slam is outclassed by Return and Body Slam in terms of both power and accuracy. Slam also does not have a secondary effect to make it stand out, making it even more outclassed by the two.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/return">Return</a> is stronger.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/double-edge">Double-Edge</a> is much stronger and has recoil damage.</p>